 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EUserful is making desktop computing more affordable\u0026#8230; and accessible.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EUserful Corporation is the world\u0026#8217;s leading Linux desktop virtualization company with millions of users in over 100 countries. The company\u0026#8217;s software which turns 1 computer into 20+, lowers desktop computing costs, improves manageability, and reduces both electricity consumption and e-waste.  \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EUserful\u0026#8217;s software is sold through a partner network of resellers and OEMs worldwide.  With over 800,000 seats sold, Userful software is used in over 100 countries from schools and libraries to hotels and Internet cafes, call centres, military and more. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ECore Products\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EUserful MultiSeat Linux\u2122 is a complete classroom computer software bundle that turns 1 Linux computer into 20+ high performance independent computer stations. It includes the Edubuntu operating system for schools, classroom computer management tools, and dozens of education specific applications in a single install. It enables schools to quickly deploy large numbers of computer stations for a very low cost, whether in the classroom, computer lab, or school library. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EUserful MultiSeat\u2122 is multiseat Linux desktop virtualization software that can create up to 20+ independent stations from a single standard computer box by simply attaching extra monitors, keyboards and mice. It\u0026#8217;s easy to install and configure, and works with all the leading Linux distributions. Userful also offers a free 2-user version for personal use.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EUserful Desktop\u2122 is a complete public computing solution that lets clients manage, monitor, and multiply their PCs. It takes the headache out of public computing by providing a safe, secure and virus-free setting for clients. The solution includes over 40 applications supporting over 30 languages. Simple remote management makes it easy to control and customize client PCs, saving time and money.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EUserful is the industry leader in Linux MultiSeat solutions for education\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EUserful enables educators to deploy twice as many computers for the same budget. Educators and administrators from all over the world appreciate the significant combined cost savings that Linux and Userful\u0026#8217;s multiseat computing solution offer. Userful MultiSeat solutions are easy to set up, use and maintain, and provide teachers with the tools they need to give their students a high quality computer-based education.  Userful\u0026#8217;s global partners develop integrated solutions that make a positive impact towards digital inclusion in their regions while respecting the  environment. Userful\u0026#8217;s focus on what matters most to governments and educators around the world is why more than 50,000 schools in 100 countries use Userful to provide millions of students with computer access.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EUserful is setting the standard for green computing \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EUserful is proud of being the industry leader in green computing. Turning 1 computer into 20+ reduces CO2 emissions by up to 15 tons per year per system and reduces electronic waste by up to 80%.  In 2009, customers using Userful\u0026#8217;s software that turns one PC into 20+, saved over 200,000 tonnes of CO2, the equivalent of taking more than 35,000 cars off the road, or planting 50,000 acres of trees! \u003C/p\u003E",
